nteract/165141/', '[1] "Product Information. Retevmo (selpercatinib)." Lilly, Eli and Company, Indianapolis, IN.[2] "Product Information. Retevmo (selpercatinib)." Lilly, Eli and Company, Indianapolis, IN.[3] Wohlt PD, Zheng L, Gunderson S, Balzar SA, Johnson BD, Fish JT "Recommendations for the use of medications with continuous enteral nutrition." Am J Health Syst Pharm 66 (2009): 1438-67[4] "Product Information. VFEND (voriconazole)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.', 1767363025);
